Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡就是我的秘密寶地哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,妳怎麼能發現這地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.35,0:00:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 妳身體不好就坐在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.03,0:01:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看 應該畫哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.54,0:01:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}字幕監督 牧瀬紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.69,0:02:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 沙也加前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.97,0:02:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 蒼司
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,妳這樣我很頭大的 模特兒怎麼打瞌睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的課題是畫彼此的表情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.38,0:02:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,畫完成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法 誰叫妳在我畫的時候睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,倒是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,蒼司
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,來寫生外面的風景怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,反正這是自習課
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 白河老師的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是以死與女性為主題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他還沒讓我們看到真的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,蒼司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,到外面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,外面一定很舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那幅風景畫吸引了我的眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,經由它 我感受到畫家白河律遺傳的才華
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可是不知為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就是沒有向日葵的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說他最討厭向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他不告訴人理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,對我當然也不透露了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,妳要不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你是蒼司前輩是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？難道妳是若林的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我是美繪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,若林美繪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我哥哥在綜合醫院當醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩你有沒有女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才說的話請你忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 我是有事找前輩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我好擔心蒼司前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那個畫家…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你還是別靠近那種只畫屍體的畫家比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,外面謠傳很糟糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說他為了自己的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,親手殺死模特兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好險好險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 妳是何時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,妳幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼蒼司前輩 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,來 冰激淩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有點融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我到車站附近那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,專程買過來給你吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,蒼司 你總是那樣子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,總是？那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道該怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才真的是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那我來確認看看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,原來接吻會讓人心跳加快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,妳的心跳得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,蒼司
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,蒼司
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,蒼司 你不可以離開我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我絕不會離開妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真的…永遠和我在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次看到那孩子這樣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 我有個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看老師的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,看我的畫？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看老師真正的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就是…屍體的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為我不會再畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是看過你的畫 我改變主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,請問您去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,走了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一起喝咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我買了好咖啡豆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事 蒼司
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼妳那麼討厭他 他是妳的父親啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,誰叫他要殺死媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 關於這件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,請用 蒼司畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,村子有奇怪的謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道真相
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:12:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那是讓人一言難盡的可怕的一幅畫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,妳等一下 我馬上喊爸爸過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,沙也加 妳回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可是媽媽她…她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸還有非做不可的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那時候我覺得自己好像看到了惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那時候馬上送去醫院的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽可能就不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可是他卻畫起了媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,其實如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,當然我沒有帶媽媽去向日葵花田的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,果然 還是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那並不是妳的錯呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,妳媽媽一定是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,蒼司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,白河先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是白河律
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他為什麼來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,白河先生 這個藥性很強 使用時請多加留心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是毒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,蒼司 我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎 進去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡可以坐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以看到我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,可以看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,妳底子不算壞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 怕我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不 沒那回事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.87,0:17:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我比較想吃烤地瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,今天很晚了 在這裡告別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,別客氣 我送你回家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,最近外面很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那就更不該來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,明天天氣如果不錯 我們一起去野餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,野餐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,帶著便當
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,到那裡畫圖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那也準備泳裝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一起游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,請別忘記帶寫生簿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我來接妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我們約個地方碰面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 就那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我…第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 我在那裡等妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,美女唷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你們搞過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,也讓我們分享好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可以只有你一個人獨享
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,反正她的老爸是殺人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你說誰是殺人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我要抗議一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,畫人物畫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,必須先瞭解人體結構
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,肌肉 臟器 血管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,知道關節動作與身高協調的重心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要讓人失去平衡就太輕而易舉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這次我放過你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果你們還想對我的作品下手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我就殺死你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我的…作品？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 我有事跟你談
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在想去給媽媽掃墓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 為什麼總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道今天是媽媽的忌日的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那不重要 沙也加
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我有事跟妳談
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我談？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 談很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,今天你幾點回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想浪費晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定要連絡哦 昨天你一直沒回來吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 上代家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 請問妳是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,若林？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我是說 趕快轉給前輩 我有急事找他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:21:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很不巧 大哥現在外出中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,誰呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你要談什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我想請妳現在當我作畫的模特兒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,美繪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.73,0:21:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,蒼司前輩 我找了你好久
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 你沒有事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有事？怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,上次我在醫院看到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那個畫家買了「劇藥」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.88,0:21:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為是用來害你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.82,0:21:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,劇藥？律老師買那種藥做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 請開門
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.83,0:22:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 妳在裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.18,0:22:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,有某種味道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.98,0:22:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,血？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.79,0:22:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 妳在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 律老師
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.46,0:22:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.39,0:22:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是血跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,蒼司
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.75,0:22:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.57,0:23:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.44,0:23:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.25,0:23:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,蒼司？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.98,0:23:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.52,0:23:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.86,0:23:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.59,0:23:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.26,0:23:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.74,0:23:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.27,0:23:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,老師的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.27,0:23:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是老師的字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.74,0:24:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,當你看到這封信時
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.88,0:24:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我應該已經不在人世了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.28,0:24:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不 其實我的命運註定我早該如此
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.69,0:24:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經癌症末期了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.69,0:24:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,發現得太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.70,0:24:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,諷刺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.57,0:24:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這次換我自己成為屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.37,0:24:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我的畫全是幻想出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.18,0:24:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一的例外是妻子的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.78,0:24:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢發誓 這並不是我希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.32,0:24:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是妻子留下遺言 想要成就我的藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.99,0:24:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 卻因此讓沙也加痛苦不已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.26,0:24:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我死期逼近了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.33,0:24:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,過著用藥物來壓抑痛苦的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.00,0:25:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就在這時候
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.61,0:25:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那個女人出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.67,0:25:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她說要讓我死前達成最後心願
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.28,0:25:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,身為畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.62,0:25:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我最後的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.48,0:25:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是把沙也加留在畫布中
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.09,0:25:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是沙也加恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.69,0:25:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒機會畫
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.23,0:25:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就在這時候 蒼司 你出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.23,0:25:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看到你的畫 我想 我可以畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.77,0:25:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然這方面有點過激
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.64,0:25:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我用安眠藥讓沙也加睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.18,0:25:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,以她為模特兒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.64,0:25:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,因為今天是我活著的最後一天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.78,0:25:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我與那位女性的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.78,0:25:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,蒼司 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.39,0:25:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,沙也加就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.92,0:25:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,白河律
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.79,0:25:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.13,0:26:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸…
